
Kubernetes deployment locally setup
ingress
kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes/ingress-nginx/main/deploy/static/provider/cloud/deploy.yaml

install cert manager
kubectl apply -f https://github.com/jetstack/cert-manager/releases/download/v1.10.0/cert-manager.yaml

apply using kubectl
kubectl apply -f ./k8



kubernetes worflow is performed on self host
used local docker desktop kubernetes cluster 
local desktop listens in on workflow triggers and is defined as runner


